{"tid":1441963,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［勇武入］今日班快閃撚到底想點樣","createTime":"2019-08-10T19:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T05:26:24.000Z","uid":12517,"like":46,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b82cebf9b1326d69005de0637595c7a1b261a32d","tid":1441963,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:15:21.000Z","msg":"你地攞住大聲公亂叫人走，係大圍就叫人去紅磡，又唔解釋原因。好，大圍唔岩守，我地咪轉場去沙田；沙田防線都未set完，又叫人去紅磡，我問個大聲公點解去紅磡，佢都係唔肯解釋唔肯溝通，淨話：「你地可以照樣留低。」<br />\n<br />\n大佬你帶住成大班人走，留低既點算？同埋有一部分留低既根本唔明咩事要走，你地唔同其他義士溝通，淨叫人走到底想點？想快閃都比個空間其他人跟呀。最後我地留低既傾左個共識：去黃大仙幫手。<br />\n<br />\n點知去到又有大聲公叫人去九龍灣。果時大家都好燥，出到黎好似比人耍咁，乜都做唔到，好多手足嬲住返屋企。<br />\n<br />\n你地攞得大聲公，就更加要顧及其他人意見，就算達成唔到共識都要同傾下，起碼其他義士跟得上、知道你地想點先。<br />\n<br />\n少少反省：<br />\n<br />\n好多義士都缺乏計劃撤退路線意識。快閃每一個地方、點樣set路障都要首先考慮逃生路線，無理由路障set到封撚埋自己撤退路線嫁（5/8沙田、今日大圍都有呢個問題），手足必定要熟悉逃生路線！<br />\n<br />\n今日快閃左好多地方（大埔、大圍、沙田、黃大仙、九龍灣），但d狗永遠快過我地到，做好晒部署，快閃已經唔太work。<br />\n<br />\n今日發左個惡夢，個夢好失敗，好驚聽日重蹈覆轍。<br />\n<br />\n利申：以上係發夢內容"},{"pid":"3dce0b91ae898d5e46a43f85ac1343e1f8f4f228","tid":1441963,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c6a8d70f351b95b972dd71ace42a6af38262a9","tid":1441963,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6361540b42dc67e246e98e07909b7f0f4b94d2","tid":1441963,"uid":12517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:18:05.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdc1f335791ed31427623e514d62dc9f7f88b95","tid":1441963,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:18:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9be0ee74fabe728e093171ec03af0512ccc695ba","tid":1441963,"uid":10289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:18:57.000Z","msg":"唔反對快閃<br />\n但前線手足要保持冷靜<br />\n<br />\n喺冷靜嘅同時不彷諗下點樣利用手上文宣核彈<br />\n<br />\n［文宣唔夠快］［地區工作］可唔可以俾啲時間文宣組？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441906</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"08534fdb7e978bb9e4c848df3a330488bd8d2831","tid":1441963,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:20:58.000Z","msg":"好傷心"},{"pid":"45771e6c0dc621985100a4d62d6d842b7a69b030","tid":1441963,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08d19624daf3f365df640e9e9cb36855e7d84d0","tid":1441963,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587eb88c69ac2a751ee0fae6b57723e8f68114d5","tid":1441963,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3306b9c210ee4dce8e7885d0f5fc59b88164cf","tid":1441963,"uid":294052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:23:13.000Z","msg":"無論任何時候 前線手足一定要諗撤退路線"},{"pid":"4117839730feb382cdc2596182c1e07351e8e38c","tid":1441963,"uid":12517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:24:47.000Z","msg":"路障唔好再封埋撤退路線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd03f5623749cd314fea3f2f47483ef283e30c2","tid":1441963,"uid":12517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:25:12.000Z","msg":"路障唔好封撤退路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5bb58bde521f16d3ebab0d6d56355bad284d0cd","tid":1441963,"uid":12517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:25:33.000Z","msg":"求你地 路障唔好封撤退路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" c